overview: The user wanted to elevate the aesthetics of their sleep questionnaire
  app, which they felt was too generic. The agent initiated a thorough review of
  the app's visual design, identifying issues with its color palette,
  backgrounds, form elements, and overall visual interest. A new strategy was
  developed to introduce a calming, sleep-themed aesthetic using deep indigos,
  purples, and teals. The agent then systematically updated the global CSS, main
  questionnaire form, progress bar, intro section, and all form field components
  (checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders). Crucially, all section groupings were
  transformed from plain gray boxes to visually appealing, themed cards. The
  report section also received significant styling improvements. The outcome is
  a professional, engaging, and visually consistent application that better
  reflects its purpose as a sleep health assessment tool.
